# NOTE ON DATA FILES:
# The full generated dataset is ~85MB (140K-row monthly panel + processed
# features), too heavy to check into git sensibly. It's excluded below and
# regenerated by running the pipeline (see README "Quickstart" -- 3 commands,
# ~90 seconds total). Trained model binaries (~2MB, small) ARE checked in
# so the Streamlit app works immediately after clone without requiring a
# full retrain first.
data/raw/*.csv
data/processed/*.csv
powerbi/exports/*.csv
